<h2>Why the free plan isn't enough</h2>
<div class="insight">
<div class="tag">✓ What you lose on the free plan</div>
<ul class="checklist">
<li>1 chart per tab: no multi-timeframe side-by-side analysis without swapping layouts manually</li>
<li>2 indicators per chart: not enough for any real technical setup</li>
<li>1 price alert that expires in 60 days: practically unusable for set-and-monitor strategies</li>
<li>No webhook support: alerts can notify you, but can't trigger anything</li>
<li>5,000 bars of history: too thin for meaningful backtesting</li>
<li>No second-based intervals: intraday precision work not available</li>
