<h2>One thing to know about futures data</h2>
<p>CME Group instruments (ES, NQ, MES, MNQ, CL, GC, RTY, YM) are 10 minutes delayed on all subscription tiers by default — including paid plans. Real-time CME data is a separate add-on: $7/month for non-professional users. If you're day trading futures, that $7 is not optional. Factor it into your real monthly cost.</p>

